						<p>Experimac Sandy Springs, GA offers professional Apple<sup>&reg;</sup> related services throughout the Atlanta area. We buy, sell, trade and repair Apple<sup>&reg;</sup> Macintosh<sup>&reg;</sup> computers, iPhone<sup>&reg;</sup> and iPad<sup>&reg;</sup>, and offer some of the best pricing available anywhere for Apple<sup>&reg;</sup> products and repairs. Experimac has worked on everything from iPad<sup>&reg;</sup> to iPhone<sup>&reg;</sup>, to MacBook<sup>&reg;</sup> and iMac<sup>&reg;</sup>, from iOS to OS X<sup>&reg;</sup>.</p>
<p>Experimac is the&nbsp;<a href="find-us-atlanta-ga-area">Atlanta</a> area authority on Apple<sup>&reg;</sup> product repairs, and trade-ins. We offer a wide selection of refurbished desktop and laptop Apple<sup>&reg;</sup> Macintosh<sup>&reg;</sup> computers and devices.</p>
<p>Experimac performs all out of warranty repairs on Apple<sup>&reg;</sup> computers and other devices including upgrading Macintosh<sup>&reg;</sup> computers with higher capacity storage, installing more memory (RAM), replacing logic boards, and performing just about any other Apple<sup>&reg;</sup> repair that you may need done.</p>
<p>Our team of experts have heard it all, from iPhone<sup>&reg;</sup> and iPad<sup>&reg;</sup> flying off the roof of a moving car to taking a swim in the ocean. Whether you are looking to trade, buy, sell an Apple<sup>&reg;</sup> product or just need to&nbsp;<a href="repairs-and-upgrades/iphone/">repair</a> your glass screen on your iPhone<sup>&reg;</sup> or iPad<sup>&reg;</sup>, stop by our <a href="find-us-sandy-springs-ga-office">Sandy Springs</a>, GA Experimac store today for a free quote!</p>
